1: INSTALL - OSC ARDUINO LIBRARY 
2: ARDUINO LOAD - ESP8266sendMessage EXAMPLE
3: ARDUINO CHANGE - ESP8266sendMessage CODE
	- NETWORK ACCESS (NEED TO BE THE SAME NETWORK AS MAX/MSP COMPUTER CONNECTION )
	- IP-REMOTE ADRESS (FROM THE MAX/MSP/M4L COMPUTER)
4: MAX/MSP/ M4L - load "receive osc.maxpat"
5: Check OSC Connection

MANDATORY:
OSC ARDUINO LIBRARY – INCLUDE -> https://github.com/CNMAT/OSC
ODOT OSC LIBRARY (MAX/MSP) – INCLUDE -> https://cnmat.berkeley.edu/downloads
